history.text: Hello
hello friend, are you interested in iron man?
IDK, tell me a bit more about it
have you seen it?
It stars Robert Downey Jr and Terrance Howard. It was made in 2008.
Oh, yeah,. I've heard about that one, would it be worth checking out...your personal opinion?
i have seen it. it is impressive.
jon favreau directed it, it is funny as well as action packed.
gwenyth paltrow stars as pepper potts, tonys secretary and love interest.
I've always enjoyed Downey, Jr! And movies that are action packed and funny
Oh Gwenth! I wondered who was the female actor..she rocks~!
well, i mean it has 94% on rotten tomatoes, so you know its pretty good.
Gwenyth is definitely a winning actress
the special effects are really polished too.
especially to receive a 94% there, it confirms and passes my test then    Special Effects..the things they do today with computerized special effects seems under rated

it doesn't feel like a normal comic movie,it has a military feel to it. i liked it a 
lot.
Wonderful, I wondered what was your take on it
i think robert downeys take on tony stark was as good as we will ever get. that is for sure.
Does Gwenyth do a few action packed stunts herself?
that's a powerful admonition...I like that
she has a few for sure she is terrific. her wit is evident.
Thanks for the heads' up, I know for sure that I will include it in my list of top movies to check out
....See You At The Movies!  lol   Bye
awesome! thanks a bunch!
You are more than welcome
jeff bridges plays obadiah stane. that is a neat name. i like it.
Obadian Stane?  That does have a ring to it, like power and magic all mixed up into one, sounds like.
Is he the villian?
the plot is really good, it manages to be simple but still keep you on your toes.
i think so. i havent seen it in a minute.
he blows up a house with people in it. it is bananas.
yeah, sounds like that's very bananas...then Downey kicks his butt for doing that?
oh, wait, you said you've not seen it, yet? Right?
yeah stark goes nutso after that. lots of iron man fighting.
his suit is awesome. lots of technology.
I wonder if it also involves rescuing Pepper Pots
coool !
indeed it does.
FAN-tastic!

uid2response.feedback: With giving more info regarding the plots, and what to expect, I'm convinced that Iron Man would be well worth tuning in to.
